    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Culmina<lb break="no" n="2"/>li pro <expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>ute</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></del> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Ul<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Super de<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Karn</abbr><ex>unti</ex></expan> a<lb break="no" n="6"/>edilicius un<lb break="no" n="7"/>a cum <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Maximo fili<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zeile 1 befindet sich auf der corona, Zeile 10 auf der crepido. Auf der corona über Zeile 1 ist auf einigen Fotos ein in roter Farbe aufgemaltes O zu erkennen. I in Zeile 9 in L eingeschrieben. Datierung: Nach Kremer erscheint Karnuntum mit K erst ab 202.</p>
            </div>
